---
// BoutiquePhilosophySection component - Single Responsibility: Philosophy display
const { id } = Astro.props;
---

<section
  id={id}
  class="py-24 md:py-32 px-8 bg-primary text-on-primary relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <svg
      class="w-full h-full"
      viewBox="0 0 400 400"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <path
        d="M0,200 Q100,0 200,200 T400,200"
        fill="none"
        stroke="white"
        stroke-width="2"></path>
      <path
        d="M0,220 Q100,20 200,220 T400,220"
        fill="none"
        stroke="white"
        stroke-width="1"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20">
      <div>
        <span
          class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-tertiary-fixed-dim block mb-6 font-bold"
        >
          Filosofía Boutique
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-10 leading-tight">
          Traje a medida, no modelos <span
            class="italic text-tertiary-fixed-dim">enlatados.</span
          >
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-tertiary-fixed-dim flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="text-tertiary-fixed-dim"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                d="M200-160v-240h80v160h160v80H200Zm320 0v-80h160v-160h80v240H520ZM160-520v-240h240v80H240v160h-80Zm560 0v-160H560v-80h240v240h-80ZM320-320v-320h320v320H320Zm80-80h160v-160H400v160Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl mb-3">Diseño Personalizado</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed font-body">
              Cada intervención se construye desde cero, respetando la
              singularidad biológica y psíquica del paciente.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-tertiary-fixed-dim flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="text-tertiary-fixed-dim"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                d="M480-80q-80 0-150-30t-122-82q-52-52-82-122t-30-150q0-78 29-147t80-121l49 61q-34 40-52 90t-18 104q0 119 82.5 203T480-160q11 0 22-1t21-3l12 78q-18 4-37 5t-38 1Zm181-80-60-60q21-13 40-29t36-35l60 52q-23 26-49 47.5T661-160Zm115-161-55-58q14-20 25-42.5t18-46.5l77 22q-11 36-28.5 69.5T776-321Zm44-245-78-14q4-24 5-47t-2-47l79-11q6 32 7.5 66t-11.5 73ZM676-788l-27-75q34-14 69-21t71-3l-10 80q-26-2-51.5 3.5T676-788Zm-196 28q-66 0-113-47t-47-113q0-66 47-113t113-47q66 0 113 47t47 113q0 66-47 113t-113 47Zm0-80q33 0 56.5-23.5T560-920q0-33-23.5-56.5T480-1000q-33 0-56.5 23.5T400-920q0 33 23.5 56.5T480-840Zm-214 16-56-56q35-36 80.5-57.5T387-1060l21 77q-35 12-65.5 28.5T266-824Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl mb-3">Subjetividad como Dato</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed font-body">
              No solo tratamos patologías; escuchamos al sujeto detrás del
              síntoma para una recuperación sostenible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-tertiary-fixed-dim flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="text-tertiary-fixed-dim"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                d="M280-520q-33 0-56.5-23.5T200-600q0-33 23.5-56.5T280-680q33 0 56.5 23.5T360-600q0 33-23.5 56.5T280-520Zm400 0q-33 0-56.5-23.5T600-600q0-33 23.5-56.5T680-680q33 0 56.5 23.5T760-600q0 33-23.5 56.5T680-520ZM480-120q-33 0-56.5-23.5T400-200q0-33 23.5-56.5T480-280q33 0 56.5 23.5T560-200q0 33-23.5 56.5T480-120Zm0-440q-33 0-56.5-23.5T400-640q0-33 23.5-56.5T480-720q33 0 56.5 23.5T560-640q0 33-23.5 56.5T480-560Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl mb-3">Sincronía Disciplinaria</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed font-body">
              El médico, el psiquiatra y el psicólogo trabajan en tiempo real,
              no en silos aislados.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
